Inge Morath, Cynthia Balfour Rehearsing "Fire Vanquished By Snow," 1955 [DETAIL]

Archival Digital C-print stamped and authorized by the Inge Morath Foundation

Dimensions: 26.25 x 18" [sheet size: 30.25" x 22"]

Edition of 30

Limited-edition print from a photograph from 1955 by the photographer Inge Morath. The image is from Morath's "Bal d'hiver" series, which was featured in Esopus 17.

LEARN MORE ABOUT EDITION

This edition is offered as a gift in exchange for a donation of $2,500 or more to the Esopus Foundation Ltd. Please note that $1,250 of this donation is tax-deductible. You will receive a letter of receipt for your records. Visit our Donations page for more information.
